data.description:
!!!!!THIS BRICK BEAUTY IS A MUST SEE!!!!!


Come see this 2 bedroom, 2.5 bath townhome located in a stylish gated community.


It is located in the heart of Jacksonville!!! Shopping malls, restaurants, and easy accessible highways are just a few attractions.  Throughout downstairs luxury vinyl plank flooring was installed. This home has spacious bedrooms on the second floor, with each having it's on private bathroom.9 The screened in porch and pond is ideal for relaxation and quiet time. This home also includes access to the Kendall Pointe amenity center including pool, exercise facility, and club house.
